Package io.sourceforge.curtthomas.isbn

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JsonIsbn
    Writes one or more JSON strings containing an International Standard Book Numbers components to standard output when invoked.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Isbn
    Constants corresponding to the data at https://www.isbn-international.org/range_file_generation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CannotInferPrefixException
    Thrown by the Isbn type's getComponent(), allComponentsMinKeys(), and allComponentsAddedKeys() methods when the code cannot infer a prefix for an ISBN based on RangeMessage.xml.
    PoorISBNDataException
    Thrown by the Isbn type's isbnThirteen() method when an ISBN has missing or extraneous digits, or is thirteen digits long but does not begin with either 978 or 979.
